Note:
Runa Standard Library: Compile-Time Reflection Optimization Module

Production-grade compile-time reflection optimization system providing static analysis,
pre-computed reflection metadata, and advanced compilation-time optimizations.
Eliminates runtime reflection overhead through static analysis and code generation,
surpassing Java's compile-time processors, C#'s Source Generators, and Rust's macros.

Features:
- Static reflection metadata pre-computation
- Compile-time type analysis and optimization
- Automatic reflection cache pre-population
- Static method dispatch optimization
- Compile-time generic instantiation
- Dead code elimination for unused reflection
- Optimal reflection call site generation
- Cross-module reflection optimization
:End Note

Import "collections" as Collections
Import "datetime/datetime" as DateTime
Import "string" as String
Import "reflection/types" as Types
Import "reflection/methods" as Methods
Import "compiler/ir/ir" as IR

Note: Compile-time optimization data structures
Type called "CompileTimeOptimizer":
    optimizer_id as String
    compilation_unit as CompilationUnit
    reflection_analysis as ReflectionAnalysis
    optimizations as List[ReflectionOptimization]
    generated_code as List[GeneratedCode]
    metadata_cache as CompileTimeMetadataCache
    configuration as OptimizationConfig

Type called "CompilationUnit":
    unit_id as String
    source_files as List[String]
    dependencies as List[String]
    reflection_sites as List[ReflectionSite]
    type_definitions as List[Types.TypeDescriptor]
    method_definitions as List[Methods.MethodDescriptor]
    optimization_opportunities as List[OptimizationOpportunity]

Type called "ReflectionSite":
    site_id as String
    location as SourceLocation
    reflection_type as ReflectionType
    target_type as Optional[Types.TypeDescriptor]
    target_method as Optional[Methods.MethodDescriptor]
    usage_frequency as Integer
    optimization_potential as OptimizationPotential
    static_resolvable as Boolean

Type called "SourceLocation":
    file_path as String
    line_number as Integer
    column_number as Integer
    source_span as SourceSpan

Type called "SourceSpan":
    start_line as Integer
    start_column as Integer
    end_line as Integer
    end_column as Integer

Type ReflectionType is:
    | TypeIntrospection
    | MethodInvocation
    | PropertyAccess
    | FieldAccess
    | AttributeQuery
    | GenericInstantiation
    | DynamicCasting
    | InterfaceQuery

Type OptimizationPotential is:
    | High
    | Medium
    | Low
    | None

Type called "ReflectionAnalysis":
    analysis_id as String
    hot_paths as List[ReflectionHotPath]
    cold_paths as List[String]
    static_resolutions as List[StaticResolution]
    optimization_candidates as List[OptimizationCandidate]
    performance_impact as PerformanceImpact
    recommendations as List[OptimizationRecommendation]

Type called "ReflectionHotPath":
    path_id as String
    call_frequency as Integer
    execution_time_ms as Float
    memory_allocations as Integer
    reflection_sites as List[String]
    optimization_priority as Integer

Type called "StaticResolution":
    site_id as String
    original_reflection_call as String
    resolved_type as Types.TypeDescriptor
    resolved_method as Optional[Methods.MethodDescriptor]
    resolution_confidence as Float
    optimization_applied as Boolean

Type called "OptimizationCandidate":
    candidate_id as String
    site_id as String
    optimization_type as OptimizationType
    potential_improvement as Float
    implementation_complexity as ComplexityLevel
    risk_assessment as RiskLevel

Type OptimizationType is:
    | StaticDispatch
    | InlineExpansion
    | ConstantFolding
    | DeadCodeElimination
    | CachePrePopulation
    | GenericSpecialization
    | VirtualCallDevirtualization

Type ComplexityLevel is:
