    | Simple
    | Moderate
    | Complex
    | VeryComplex

Type RiskLevel is:
    | VeryLow
    | Low
    | Medium
    | High
    | VeryHigh

Type called "PerformanceImpact":
    baseline_performance as Float
    optimized_performance as Float
